Summary: 
 * Merge from SystemC-Examples--mainline--0.5 branch
 - Added missing $(auxdir)/jfrules.mk include
   this provides a default doxygen-doc target which does nothing
 - Added LICENSE and COPYRIGHT files
 - Added copyright boilerplate from COPYRIGHT to all files
   except files in mpeg4-ref and idct2d-ref
 - add verbose output, so that each actor writes its input and outputs
 - for software synthesis, for each actor type it can be specified, whether
   this output shall take place or not.
 - explicit code for problemgraph generation is no longer needed
 - Eliminate from the sc_main function of all examples the now obsolete
   (From SysteMoC--mainline--0.4--patch-126
    and  SysteMoC--event-scheduler--0.5--patch-35 onwards)
   --generate-problemgraph checking code.
 - Eliminated --generate-problemgraph code from design-src-snk-noconsume.cpp
 - Split systemoc-mpeg4 into systemoc-idct2d and systemoc-mpeg4

